    <p>
      Highlighting the logo's individual elements and our attention to detail
      throughout the branding process, this was Code Freedom's first message to
      the world in 2024, teasing upcoming events for the Apex Legends and
      Counter-Strike communities, and generating hype around the forthcoming
      circuit.
    </p>
